*INCLUDE zmodularisation_04_set_dataf01.



*MACROS
*DATA : lv_output TYPE I.
*
*PARAMETERS : p_input1 TYPE I.
*PARAMETERS : p_input2 TYPE I.
*PARAMETERS : p_r1 TYPE C RADIOBUTTON GROUP r1.
*PARAMETERS : p_r2 TYPE C RADIOBUTTON GROUP r1.
*PARAMETERS : p_r3 TYPE C RADIOBUTTON GROUP r1.
*
*DEFINE operation. "MACROS
*WRITE :'The output is' , &1. "Macro With Placeholders use & (max 9)- to pass values at runtime
* END-OF-DEFINITION.
*
*IF p_r1 = 'X'.
*lv_output = p_input1 + p_input2.
*operation lv_output.
*ENDIF.
*
*IF p_r2 = 'X'.
*lv_output = p_input1 - p_input2.
*operation lv_output.
*ENDIF.
*
*IF p_r3 = 'X'.
*lv_output = p_input1 * p_input2.
*operation lv_output.
*ENDIF.


